4 Ihaivam ekā kaṇṭhikā baddhā
5 parvata-paridhiḥ, yathā prathamaiva;
6 anyathā tu tasya cakraṃ śīghram eva namayati.

13 Tataḥ sa sūryam prati dṛṣṭim niyuktaḥ cakāra;
14 dakṣiṇa-pakṣam pradakṣiṇā-madhyam cakāra,
15 vāma-pakṣam sva-pakṣāt vinivṛttaḥ cakāra.

19 Tvam jagat tāpasi, tvam tasminn eva prakāśase;
20 yadi viparītaḥ ko’pi hetur na bhavati,
21 tava kiraṇāḥ sadā eva netāraḥ bhavanti.

22 Yāvatraikam sahasram iha gaṇyate,
23 tāvat tatra vayam adhunā gatāḥ sma,
24 alpasaṃkṣiptena kālena, icchāyāḥ prabalatvāt;

40 Viparītaśabdasya lagamo bhavitavyam;
41 manye yathā mama matiḥ,
42 kṣamāyāḥ padam prāpnuvanti pūrvam eva tvam śṛṇuṣyasi.

52 Na manye yadi prthivyām adya
53 puruṣaḥ kaścid evaṃ kathinaḥ syāt, yaḥ na syāt
54 karuṇayā vihvalaḥ tena yat paścāt apaśyam;

67 Yathā ca andhebhyaḥ sūryaḥ na prayojanam asti,
68 Tathā tatra chāyāsu, yāsu aham adhunā bruve,
69 Divyaṃ prakāśaḥ svayam dātum na icchati;

76 Saḥ suṣṭhu veda yadi vāg-vikalpaḥ kim abhidhātum icchati;
77 atas tasya praśnam na pratikṣate sma,
78 kim tu āha: "Bruhi, sañkṣiptaṃ ca vivakṣitaṃ ca."

79 Virgilio mām āgacchat asmāt paścāt
80 pṛṣṭhasya yasya patanam sambhavati,
81 yataḥ kaścit api ādhāraḥ na āveṣṭayati;

91 bruta me, yataḥ mama priyaṃ bhaviṣyati priyam ca,
92 yadi jīvaḥ atra bhavān lāṭīnaḥ;
93 ca api tadīyaṃ śreyaḥ syāt yadi aham jānāmi tām."

145 "Aha ayam śravaṇe eva navaḥ arthaḥ asti,"
146 pratyuttaram adāt, "yad bhagavān tava prema karoti iti mahatī niśānī asti;
147 atas tava prārthanayā kadācit mama sukham bhavati.
